snippet.title: FixFox Launch Trailer
snippet.description: In FixFox, you play as Vix, an unlucky space mechanic, who crash-lands on a planet where tools are forbidden. Accompanied by her trusty toolbox, Vix travels across the planet discovering hidden stashes left by pirates, making repairs, and sampling tasty local delicacies. Out now! https://www.fixfoxgame.com/ #indiegames #gaming #steam
